                            <comment id="16358806" author="tallison@mitre.org" created="Fri, 9 Feb 2018 18:46:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you for opening this.  To save us some time...can you tell us where we&apos;re catching the RuntimeException?  &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16358843" author="tallison@mitre.org" created="Fri, 9 Feb 2018 19:21:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry.  Found it in ZipContainerDetector&apos;s detectOPCBased...as was pointed out in by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tvernum&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tvernum&quot;&gt;tvernum&lt;/a&gt; in his comment on the ES issue &amp;lt;face_palm/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16358864" author="tallison@mitre.org" created="Fri, 9 Feb 2018 19:44:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Small fix...but see &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-2572&quot; title=&quot;Review overly broad catches&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;TIKA-2572&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;TIKA-2572&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for broader code review.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let us know what else you find.  Thank you!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
