                            <comment id="16358958" author="hudson" created="Fri, 9 Feb 2018 21:11:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;SUCCESS: Integrated in Jenkins build Tika-trunk #1435 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/Tika-trunk/1435/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/Tika-trunk/1435/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
